reviewText:
This was actually an entertaining western with Sheena actress Irish McCalla as a sadistic buxom gunslinger all dressed in black. Irish's acting was pretty good as she conveys a meaness here whereas in Sheena she was quite kind.

Irish's agent should have seen her niche was playing larger than life characters in costume.
Irish looks Great in this movie, a far different part than Sheena, she playsa bad woman of the old west, it is a refreshing movie to view.
